com.ecom.support

Class BrowserActions

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ecom.support.BrowserActions

  • public class BrowserActions
extends java.lang.Object
    Wrapper for Selenium WebDriver actions which will be performed on browser Wrappers are provided with exception handling which throws Skip Exception on occurrence of NoSuchElementException
